{"tid":1124134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國擬對中國鋼製輪圈徵收高額關稅","createTime":"2019-04-25T00:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T07:03:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"555940af5fe02aa58957ee4b17349e5416f977aa","tid":1124134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:18:35.000Z","msg":"美國擬對中國鋼製輪圈徵收高額關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454410-20190425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454410-20190425.htm&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=5755d597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1454410-20190425.htm&h=818fc5c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1454410-20190425.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國際貿易委員會表示，認定中國卡車鋼製輪圈生產企業在美國市場傾銷，並接受政府不公平補貼，對美國同類企業造成損害，將對這些產品徵收的高額關稅鎖定五年。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部在上月，裁定對所有中國鋼製輪圈生產的企業，徵收百分之321的反傾銷關稅以及百分之457的反補貼關稅。有關決定包括從中國進口、用於中型和大型卡車及其他商用車輛的22.5吋及24.5吋鋼製輪圈。美國在2017年進口總值這種商品達3.88億美元。"},{"pid":"ef3a31107b96cdfa1c92f89c9afad0f4240752e3","tid":1124134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef6bac98bbd8ec13f247a9ea33410b478a43652","tid":1124134,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"全部支那產品都收重稅啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769304dabd8a9ed740205e86c1d31246a2fb24b5","tid":1124134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}